Danielle TIRENDI, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Thomas J. TIRENDI, Defendant-Petitioner. C-430 September Term 2017
080147 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 9, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001543-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
